{"tid":672148,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★關塔那摩灣囚犯爆血淚史　女獄卒逼玩3P","createTime":"2018-05-20T17:20:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-21T04:35:39.000Z","uid":19454,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"c5d3d0ce34b5555b5407e07d33db35d1ead93ebe","tid":672148,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T17:20:54.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fon.cc&d=miWuLLDKv%2BYEpPC%2FsIXZBNZqoKrPvqrE%2FsQ53lv%2BkYo%3D&h=e9da083b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">on.cc</a>東網專訊】 古巴美軍關塔那摩灣監獄一名正服刑囚犯，經過長達6年的司法訴訟，本周成功爭取出書披露在獄中被虐的駭人情節。他聲稱被兩名女盤問員強逼參與3P性愛，形容是教他「大美國式性愛」。他自言在長期精神及肉體折磨下，不斷出現幻覺。<br />\n<br />\n44歲前恐怖組織阿蓋德成員西萊希(Mohamedou Ould Slahi)，聲稱在上世紀90年代加入該組織，其後於1992年脫離。美軍指他涉嫌於1999年在洛杉磯策劃炸彈襲擊事敗，02年將他帶往關塔那摩灣監獄拘押至今。由西萊希的日記編成的新書《關塔那摩日記》(Guantanamo Diary，暫譯)，經過6年申請解禁的官司後，本周終獲准出版。<br />\n<br />\n書中披露西萊希在獄中經歷的黑暗歲月，他聲稱被強迫維持一個痛苦的姿勢連續70天，若不從便會再受皮肉之苦。此外，<span style=\"color: red;\">獄中兩名女盤問員曾性侵他，逼他玩3P，一前一後不斷摩擦他的身軀，不僅玩弄他的陽具，且不斷說髒話羞辱他。<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n絕望的西萊希曾冀望透過禱告尋求慰藉，但被獄方阻撓。西萊希聲稱在身心飽受摧殘的情況下，久而久之開始出現幻覺，幻想聽到家人的聲音，以及家鄉的音樂。然而，獄吏卻利用西萊希出現幻覺的問題，煽動他策劃逃獄或襲擊獄吏，令他瀕臨精神失常。<br />\n西萊希在書中指，在獄吏嚴刑逼供下，才被逼承認策劃多項恐襲的罪名。西萊希的代表律師指，其當事人並無被落案起訴任何罪名，要求美軍釋放他。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20150121/bknint-20150121174842318-0121_17011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fint%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20150121%2Fbknint-20150121174842318-0121_17011_001.html&d=miWuLLDKv%2BYEpPC%2FsIXZBNZqoKrPvqrE%2FsQ53lv%2BkYo%3D&h=b7f67213\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20150121/bknint-20150121174842318-0121_17011_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"4e6242da93cc5b7d908ff6590726ba55b454f227","tid":672148,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T17:21:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20150121/photo/bknint-20150121174842318-0121_17011_001_01p.jpg?183459\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fint%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20150121%2Fphoto%2Fbknint-20150121174842318-0121_17011_001_01p.jpg%3F183459&h=0fa98b61&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"48d5b43c5ae636cf09289bdccb3578f3588f7e26","tid":672148,"uid":18948,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T00:07:18.000Z","msg":"獄吏卻利用西萊希出現幻覺的問題，煽動他策劃逃獄或襲擊獄吏<br />\n<br />\n煽動？"},{"pid":"62e0b54f259153a5f6601138938168c02791991f","tid":672148,"uid":22694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T00:08:32.000Z","msg":"快點⋯⋯"},{"pid":"8e541e1d60639753adbfa66463241b652b5ff1fb","tid":672148,"uid":35598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T00:09:28.000Z","msg":"睇咗圖先答"},{"pid":"b7d9052ea77571ffcba3a34230ea50df67fd3fd7","tid":672148,"uid":51701,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T01:10:23.000Z","msg":"你班islam 豬唔係話一到歐美就春袋漲痛<br />\n<br />\n由幾個月姦到幾歲連幾十歲都唔放過咩？"},{"pid":"805e4fe81162aa5354b5ecd3dbb8a81229d71241","tid":672148,"uid":3122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T01:13:39.000Z","msg":"硬到又幾勁"},{"pid":"4b90f1d3de8f0d2e439539df633a4ef180eb2894","tid":672148,"uid":52459,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T01:14:58.000Z","msg":"咁佢賺咗了，有得屌鬼妹，肥婆都係肉，總好過被男獄卒攪"},{"pid":"c49583d80393041c4f2f0f5cf6e91e9086f09558","tid":672148,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4b90f1d3de8f0d2e439539df633a4ef180eb2894","tid":672148,"uid":52459,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T01:14:58.000Z","msg":"咁佢賺咗了，有得屌鬼妹，肥婆都係肉，總好過被男獄卒攪"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T04:15:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/norm